abstract: >-
  Code and manuscript for an empirical multi-seed study of GRPO post-training
  at sub-3B scale on a single-GPU LoRA budget, comparing English-only,
  Vietnamese-translated, and English-with-language-consistency-reward arms
  on three mathematical reasoning benchmarks (AMC-23, MATH-500, AIME-2024).
  Source code and manuscript were prepared with AI assistance (Anthropic
  Claude via Claude Code CLI); all empirical results were independently
  verified by the author. See README and VERIFICATION.md for the full
  AI-assistance disclosure.
